SELECT distinct o.name as ragioneSociale, o.fax, o.banca as denominazione, coalesce( o.account_number, '' ) || ' · ' || coalesce( o.codice_impresa_interno, '' ) as codice, o.partita_iva as partitaIva, o.codice_fiscale as codiceFiscale, o.cf_correntista as codiceIstatPrinc, o.alert as descrCodiceIstatPrinc, o.cab as descrCodiceIstatSec, o.conto_corrente as tipoAutoveicolo, o.nome_correntista as targaAutoveicolo, o.duns_type as tipoDia, o.datapresentazione as dataDia, o.date2 as dataInizioAttivita, o.contract_end as dataFineAttivita,o.data_in_carattere as tempDA, o.data_fine_carattere as tempA, o.year_started as livelloRischio, o.notes as note,o.tipo_dest as attivita, lookup_site_id.description as asl,o.nome_correntista as Targa,lts.description as tipoStruttura, tl.description as tipo_locale, tl2.description as tipo_locale2, tl3.description as tipo_locale3, lookup_contact_source.description as carattere, lookup_contact_types.description as tipologiaContatto, lookup_org_catrischio.description as categoriaOsa, lookup_requestor_stage.description as tipologiaDIA, oaleg.addrline1 as indirizzolegale, oaleg.postalcode as caplegale, oaleg.city as cittalegale, oaleg.state as provincialegale, oaleg.longitude as longitudinelegale, oaleg.latitude as latitudinelegale, oaope.addrline1 as indirizzooperativo, oaope.postalcode as capoperativo, oaope.city as cittaoperativo, oaope.state as provinciaoperativo, oaope.longitude as longitudineoperativo, oaope.latitude as latitudineoperativo, mobile.addrline1 as indirizzomobile, mobile.postalcode as capmobile, mobile.city as cittamobile, mobile.state as provinciamobile, mobile.longitude as longitudinemobile, mobile.latitude as latitudinemobile, o.email_rappresentante as emailrappr, o.telefono_rappresentante as telrappr,o.codice_fiscale_rappresentante as cfrappr, oaloc.addrline1 as indirizzolocale, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP as dataoggi, oaloc.postalcode as caplocale, oaloc.city as cittalocale, oaloc.state as provincialocale, oaloc.longitude as longitudinelocale, oaloc.latitude as latitudinelocale, oaloc2.addrline1 as indirizzolocale2, oaloc2.postalcode as caplocale2, oaloc2.city as cittalocale2, oaloc2.state as provincialocale2, oaloc2.longitude as longitudinelocale2, oaloc2.latitude as latitudinelocale2, oaloc3.addrline1 as indirizzolocale3, oaloc3.postalcode as caplocale3, oaloc3.city as cittalocale3, oaloc3.state as provincialocale3, oaloc3.longitude as longitudinelocale3, oaloc3.latitude as latitudinelocale3, op.extension as prefissoTelefono, op.number as numeroTelefono, oe.email as email, cont.namesalutation as titoloProprietario, cont.namelast as nomeProprietario, o.tipologia as tipologia, o.cognome_rappresentante || ' ' || o.nome_rappresentante as rappresentante,
lcd1.description as codiceistatsec1, lcd2.description as codiceIstatSec2, lcd3.description as codiceIstatSec3, lcd4.description as codiceIstatSec4, lcd5.description as codiceIstatSec5, lcd6.description as codiceIstatSec6, lcd7.description as codiceIstatSec7, lcd8.description as codiceIstatSec8, lcd9.description as codiceIstatSec9, lcd10.description as codiceIstatSec10,
lcd1.short_description as descr1, lcd2.short_description as descr2, lcd3.short_description as descr3, lcd4.short_description as descr4, lcd5.short_description as descr5, lcd6.short_description as descr6, lcd7.short_description as descr7, lcd8.short_description as descr8, lcd9.short_description as descr9, lcd10.short_description as descr10
FROM organization o LEFT JOIN lookup_site_id ON (o.site_id = lookup_site_id.code) LEFT JOIN lookup_contact_source ON (o.source = lookup_contact_source.code) LEFT JOIN lookup_org_catrischio ON (o.account_size = lookup_org_catrischio.code) LEFT JOIN lookup_requestor_stage ON (o.stage_id = lookup_requestor_stage.code) LEFT JOIN organization_address oaleg ON (o.org_id = oaleg.org_id and oaleg.address_type = 1) LEFT JOIN organization_address oaope ON (o.org_id = oaope.org_id and oaope.address_type = 5) LEFT JOIN organization_address oaloc ON (o.org_id = oaloc.org_id and oaloc.address_type = 6 and oaloc.address_id = $P{addressid}) LEFT JOIN organization_address oaloc2 ON (o.org_id = oaloc2.org_id and oaloc2.address_type = 6 and oaloc2.address_id = $P{addressid2}) LEFT JOIN organization_address oaloc3 ON (o.org_id = oaloc3.org_id and oaloc3.address_type = 6 and oaloc3.address_id = $P{addressid3}) LEFT JOIN organization_address mobile ON (o.org_id = mobile.org_id and mobile.address_type = 7) LEFT JOIN organization_phone op ON (o.org_id = op.org_id) left join lookup_tipo_struttura lts on (o.tipo_struttura = lts.code) LEFT JOIN organization_emailaddress oe ON (o.org_id = oe.org_id) LEFT JOIN lookup_tipo_locale tl2 ON (o.tipo_locale2 = tl2.code) LEFT JOIN lookup_tipo_locale tl3 ON (o.tipo_locale3 = tl3.code) LEFT JOIN lookup_tipo_locale tl ON (o.tipo_locale = tl.code) left JOIN la_imprese_linee_attivita lda1 ON (o.org_id = lda1.org_id and lda1.primario is false and lda1.id = $P{lda1}) left JOIN la_imprese_linee_attivita lda2 ON (o.org_id = lda2.org_id and lda2.primario is false and lda2.id = $P{lda2} ) left JOIN la_imprese_linee_attivita lda3 ON (o.org_id = lda3.org_id and lda3.primario is false and lda3.id = $P{lda3} ) left JOIN la_imprese_linee_attivita lda4 ON (o.org_id = lda4.org_id and lda4.primario is false and lda4.id = $P{lda4} ) left JOIN la_imprese_linee_attivita lda5 ON (o.org_id = lda5.org_id and lda5.primario is false and lda5.id = $P{lda5} ) left JOIN la_imprese_linee_attivita lda6 ON (o.org_id = lda6.org_id and lda6.primario is false and lda6.id = $P{lda6}) left JOIN la_imprese_linee_attivita lda7 ON (o.org_id = lda7.org_id and lda7.primario is false and lda7.id = $P{lda7}) left JOIN la_imprese_linee_attivita lda8 ON (o.org_id = lda8.org_id and lda8.primario is false and lda8.id = $P{lda8}) left JOIN la_imprese_linee_attivita lda9 ON (o.org_id = lda9.org_id and lda9.primario is false and lda9.id = $P{lda9} ) left JOIN la_imprese_linee_attivita lda10 ON (o.org_id = lda10.org_id and lda10.primario is false and lda10.id = $P{lda10})
left JOIN la_rel_ateco_attivita rat1 ON (lda1.id_rel_ateco_attivita = rat1.id) left JOIN la_rel_ateco_attivita rat2 ON (lda2.id_rel_ateco_attivita = rat2.id) left JOIN la_rel_ateco_attivita rat3 ON (lda3.id_rel_ateco_attivita = rat3.id) left JOIN la_rel_ateco_attivita rat4 ON (lda4.id_rel_ateco_attivita = rat4.id) left JOIN la_rel_ateco_attivita rat5 ON (lda5.id_rel_ateco_attivita = rat5.id) left JOIN la_rel_ateco_attivita rat6 ON (lda6.id_rel_ateco_attivita = rat6.id) left JOIN la_rel_ateco_attivita rat7 ON (lda7.id_rel_ateco_attivita = rat7.id) left JOIN la_rel_ateco_attivita rat8 ON (lda8.id_rel_ateco_attivita = rat8.id) left JOIN la_rel_ateco_attivita rat9 ON (lda9.id_rel_ateco_attivita = rat9.id) left JOIN la_rel_ateco_attivita rat10 ON (lda10.id_rel_ateco_attivita = rat10.id)
left JOIN lookup_codistat lcd1 ON (rat1.id_lookup_codistat = lcd1.code) left JOIN lookup_codistat lcd2 ON (rat2.id_lookup_codistat = lcd2.code) left JOIN lookup_codistat lcd3 ON (rat3.id_lookup_codistat = lcd3.code) left JOIN lookup_codistat lcd4 ON (rat4.id_lookup_codistat = lcd4.code) left JOIN lookup_codistat lcd5 ON (rat5.id_lookup_codistat = lcd5.code) left JOIN lookup_codistat lcd6 ON (rat6.id_lookup_codistat = lcd6.code) left JOIN lookup_codistat lcd7 ON (rat7.id_lookup_codistat = lcd7.code) left JOIN lookup_codistat lcd8 ON (rat8.id_lookup_codistat = lcd8.code) left JOIN lookup_codistat lcd9 ON (rat9.id_lookup_codistat = lcd9.code) left JOIN lookup_codistat lcd10 ON (rat10.id_lookup_codistat = lcd10.code)
LEFT JOIN contact cont LEFT JOIN contact_type_levels ctl LEFT JOIN lookup_contact_types ON (lookup_contact_types.code = ctl.type_id) ON (ctl.contact_id = cont.contact_id) ON (o.org_id = cont.org_id)
WHERE o.org_id = $P{orgid} AND o.trashed_date IS NULL
